### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/status

### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User (Replace TOKEN with actual token from login)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Monitor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/monitors
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Google Homepage",
  "url": "https://www.google.com",
  "method": "GET",
  "interval": 60,
  "timeout": 30,
  "isFavorite": true
}

### Get All Monitors
GET http://localhost:5000/api/monitors
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Monitors with Filters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/monitors?status=up&favorite=true&sort=latency-desc
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update Monitor (Replace MONITOR_ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/monitors/MONITOR_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Google Updated",
  "isFavorite": false
}

### Toggle Favorite
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/monitors/MONITOR_ID/favorite
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Toggle Active/Pause
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/monitors/MONITOR_ID/toggle
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Delete Monitor
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/monitors/MONITOR_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Health Records
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health/MONITOR_ID?timeRange=24h&limit=100
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE